rComments: This professor was AWESOME. I'm in LifeSci and took FCS195 as an elective and I absolutely loved it! By far my favourite course of the year. She's super flexible with her course content, and she's an amazingly friendly, helpful and approachable person. She really helped get my interest raring in french culture. No previous french knowledge needed.

Prof. Sandu is quite friendly and very helpful. She is approachable and presents the material in a clear and organized fashion. Always willing to help those who show some effort and the quizzes/tests tend to be fair. Study your grammar well and you should do fine. The final exam could seem intimidating, but the professor tries to prepare you well.
